করছো","audioUrl":"wbw/042_025_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27691,"position":13,"arabic":"٢٥","translation":"(২৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":26,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَجِيبُ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ وَعَمِلُوا۟ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ وَيَزِيدُهُم مِّن فَضْلِهِۦ ۚ وَٱلْكَٰفِرُونَ لَهُمْ عَذَابٌۭ شَدِيدٌۭ","translation":"and responds unto all who attain to faith and do righteous deeds; and [it is He who, in the life to come,] will give them, out of His bounty, far more [than they will have deserved], whereas for the deniers of the truth there is [but] suffering severe in store.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4298.mp3","surahId":42,"words":[{"id":28647,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَجِيبُ","translation":"এবং তিনি ডাকে সাড়া দেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28648,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28649,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান আনে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28650,"position":4,"arabic":"وَعَمِلُوا۟","translation":"ও কাজ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28651,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ","translation":"সৎ","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28652,"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَزِيدُهُم","translation":"এবং বৃদ্ধি করেন তাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28653,"position":7,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28654,"position":8,"arabic":"فَضْلِهِۦ ۚ","translation":"তাঁর অনুগ্রহ","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28656,"position":9,"arabic":"وَٱلْكَـٰفِرُونَ","translation":"এবং কাফেরদের (অবস্থা হলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28657,"position":10,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের জন্যে রয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28658,"position":11,"arabic":"عَذَابٌۭ","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28659,"position":12,"arabic":"شَدِيدٌۭ","translation":"কঠিন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_026_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28660,"position":13,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"۞ وَلَوْ بَسَطَ ٱللَّهُ ٱلرِّزْقَ لِعِبَادِهِۦ لَبَغَوْا۟ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ وَلَٰكِن يُنَزِّلُ بِقَدَرٍۢ مَّا يَشَآءُ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ بِعِبَادِهِۦ خَبِيرٌۢ بَصِيرٌۭ","translation":"For, if God were to grant [in this world] abundant sustenance to [all of] His servants, they would behave on earth with wanton insolence: but as it is, He bestows [His grace] from on high in due measure, as He wills: for, verily, He is fully aware of [the needs of] His creatures, and sees them all.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4299.mp3","surahId":42,"words":[{"id":29540,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَلَوْ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29541,"position":2,"arabic":"بَسَطَ","translation":"প্রচুর দিতেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29542,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29543,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلرِّزْقَ","translation":"জীবিকা","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29544,"position":5,"arabic":"لِعِبَادِهِۦ","translation":"তাঁর দাসদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29545,"position":6,"arabic":"لَبَغَوْا۟","translation":"তারা অবশ্যই বিপর্যয় সৃষ্টি করতো","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29546,"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29547,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29548,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِن","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29549,"position":10,"arabic":"يُنَزِّلُ","translation":"দেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29550,"position":11,"arabic":"بِقَدَرٍۢ","translation":"একটি পরিমাণ মত","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29551,"position":12,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29552,"position":13,"arabic":"يَشَآءُ ۚ","translation":"তিনি ইচ্ছে করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29554,"position":14,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29555,"position":15,"arabic":"بِعِبَادِهِۦ","translation":"তাঁর দাসদের সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29556,"position":16,"arabic":"خَبِيرٌۢ","translation":"খুব অবহিত","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29557,"position":17,"arabic":"بَصِيرٌۭ","translation":"সবকিছুই দেখেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_027_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29558,"position":18,"arabic":"٢٧","translation":"(২৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":28,"arabic":"وَهُوَ ٱلَّذِى يُنَزِّلُ ٱلْغَيْثَ مِنۢ بَعْدِ مَا قَنَطُوا۟ وَيَنشُرُ رَحْمَتَهُۥ ۚ وَهُوَ ٱلْوَلِىُّ ٱلْحَمِيدُ","translation":"And it is He who sends down rain after [men] have lost all hope, and unfolds His grace [thereby]: for He alone is [their] Protector, the One to whom all praise is due.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4300.mp3","surahId":42,"words":[{"id":30874,"position":1,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই(আল্লাহ)","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30875,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30876,"position":3,"arabic":"يُنَزِّلُ","translation":"বর্ষণ করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30877,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْثَ","translation":"বৃষ্টি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30878,"position":5,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30879,"position":6,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30880,"position":7,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30881,"position":8,"arabic":"قَنَطُوا۟","translation":"তারা নিরাশ হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30882,"position":9,"arabic":"وَيَنشُرُ","translation":"এবং বিস্তার করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30883,"position":10,"arabic":"رَحْمَتَهُۥ ۚ","translation":"তাঁর করুণা","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30885,"position":11,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনিই","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30886,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْوَلِىُّ","translation":"অভিভাবক (ওলী)","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30887,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْحَمِيدُ","translation":"প্রশংসিত","audioUrl":"wbw/042_028_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30888,"position":14,"arabic":"٢٨","translation":"(২৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":29,"arabic":"وَمِنْ ءَايَٰتِهِۦ خَلْقُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضِ وَمَا بَثَّ فِيهِمَا مِن دَآبَّةٍۢ ۚ وَهُوَ عَلَىٰ جَمْعِهِمْ إِذَا يَشَآءُ قَدِيرٌۭ","translation":"And among His signs is the [very] creation of the heavens and the earth, and of all the living creatures which He has caused to multiply throughout them: and [since He has created them,] He has [also] the power to gather them [unto Him­self] whenever He wills.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4301.mp3","surahId":42,"words":[{"id":31549,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمِنْ","translation":"এবং মধ্য হ'তে (রয়েছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31550,"position":2,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتِهِۦ","translation":"তাঁর নিদর্শনাবলীর","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31551,"position":3,"arabic":"خَلْقُ","translation":"সৃষ্টি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31552,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশের","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31553,"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31554,"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং যা কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31555,"position":7,"arabic":"بَثَّ","translation":"ছড়িয়ে দিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31556,"position":8,"arabic":"فِيهِمَا","translation":"তার উভয়ের মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31557,"position":9,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"(বিভিন্ন) ধরণের","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31558,"position":10,"arabic":"دَآبَّةٍۢ ۚ","translation":"জীবজন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31560,"position":11,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","translation":"এবং তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31561,"position":12,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31562,"position":13,"arabic":"جَمْعِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের একত্রিত করার","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31563,"position":14,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31564,"position":15,"arabic":"يَشَآءُ","translation":"তিনি ইচ্ছে করবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31565,"position":16,"arabic":"قَدِيرٌۭ","translation":"সক্ষম","audioUrl":"wbw/042_029_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":31566,"position":17,"arabic":"٢٩","translation":"(২৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":30,"arabic":"وَمَآ أَصَٰبَكُم مِّن مُّصِيبَةٍۢ فَبِمَا كَسَبَتْ أَيْدِيكُمْ وَيَعْفُوا۟ عَن كَثِيرٍۢ","translation":"Now whatever calamity may befall you [on Judgment Day] will be an outcome of what your own hands have wrought, although He pardons much;","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4302.mp3","surahId":42,"words":[{"id":32475,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"এবং যা","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32476,"position":2,"arabic":"أَصَـٰبَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের পৌঁছে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32477,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32478,"position":4,"arabic":"مُّصِيبَةٍۢ","translation":"বিপদ","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32479,"position":5,"arabic":"فَبِمَا","translation":"তা এ কারণে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32480,"position":6,"arabic":"كَسَبَتْ","translation":"কামাই করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32481,"position":7,"arabic":"أَيْدِيكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের হাতগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32482,"position":8,"arabic":"وَيَعْفُوا۟","translation":"এবং তিনি ক্ষমা করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32483,"position":9,"arabic":"عَن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32484,"position":10,"arabic":"كَثِيرٍۢ","translation":"অনেককিছু (নিজের থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/042_030_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":32485,"position":11,"arabic":"٣٠","translation":"(৩০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":31,"arabic":"وَمَآ أَنتُم بِمُعْجِزِينَ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ ۖ وَمَا لَكُم 